{"tid":112572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆乳女星去跳水節目比賽 大家都在看她的胸部","createTime":"2017-02-08T08:43:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-08T21:38:31.000Z","uid":22675,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1d4f0f45df561849d663b0106d1034d6d933b04b","tid":112572,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T08:43:14.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕西班牙女星瑪丁尼茲（Patricia Martinez）參加了跳水比賽節目，她出場時身穿深V膚色泳裝，不僅現場觀眾一飽眼福，攝影機也一直特寫她的爆乳，讓電視機前的民眾也能有滿滿的福利。<br />\n據《每日郵報》報導，瑪丁尼茲參與的跳水節目，都是由名人參賽並由專業教練指導，她跳完水後根本沒人在理主持人怎麼訪問她，因為鏡頭只Take在她的胸部上。<br />\n瑪丁尼茲此時似乎發現攝影師的行為，挑逗性地捲著頭髮擠出水滴，此時鏡頭似乎完全離不開女星的胸前，直到評分結果出來，攝影師才大夢初醒般地將鏡頭拉遠，讓裁判小組的講解得以入鏡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phprxiNHM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phprxiNHM.jpg&h=3bc25d05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1968464\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1968464&d=fAF%2FER2cs4qp%2F6NYk0BreE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=282f1ec7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1968464&h=a3295838\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1968464</a>"},{"pid":"417cdae7b5a8d6878ebe78a6dc01018639294ec9","tid":112572,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T09:12:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-4199418/Distracted-cameraman-focuses-contestant-s-boobs.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-4199418%2FDistracted-cameraman-focuses-contestant-s-boobs.html&d=fAF%2FER2cs4qp%2F6NYk0BreE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=a0728089\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-4199418/Distracted-cameraman-focuses-contestant-s-boobs.html</a>"},{"pid":"83faaa97f080